  "desc": "EA SPORTS FC 26 version 1.5.4 is dropping soon and includes the updates below.\n\n‌\n\n**Ultimate Team**\n\nMade the following changes:\n\n- Improved UI selection when viewing Player Items in a New Releases tab.\n\n- The Actions button callout was unavailable in New Releases when using the Compare Price function.\n\n‌\n\n### **Career Mode**\n\nAddressed the following issues:\n\n- Addressed an issue where CPU Slider settings would reset to default after relaunching the game and loading a save.\n\n- An incorrect team would display when starting a new Manager Career with an Icon Player.\n\n- Youth player height generation has been adjusted to ensure more realistic and balanced prospects.\n\n‌\n\n### **Clubs**\n\nAddressed the following issues: \n\n- The Objectives button opened the FC HUB instead of the Objectives screen.\n\n- Addressed instances of misaligned text.\n\n### **General, Audio, and Visual**\n\nMade the following changes:\n\n- Updated some trophy images, boots, kits, ad boards, overlays, crests, logos, star heads, hair, backdrop sponsors, anthems, stadiums, hair, banners, flags and scarves\n- [PC] Addressed some specific cases that caused game performance to drop to low frame rates after the second half.\n\n‌\n\nAddressed the following issues:\n\n- Addressed various stability issues that could have occurred.\n\n- Addressed instances of text not appearing.\n\n‌\n\nWant to provide us direct feedback about EA SPORTS FC 26? [https://go.ea.com/fc26pfp](https://go.ea.com/fc26pfp \"‌\") and let us know what you think, it only takes a few minutes.\n\n‌\n\nThanks to those who’ve provided and continue to provide feedback. Throughout the course of the EA SPORTS FC 26 season, we'll provide you with more information and updates if and when they become available. Be sure to follow \\@‌EASFCDIRECT on X as well as WhatsApp, and check out the EA SPORTS FC Tracker for the latest news and updates.\n\n‌\n\n- The EA SPORTS FC Team",
